---
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<section class="border-t border-line" aria-labelledby="join-heading">
  <div
    class="relative mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl overflow-hidden px-6 py-28 text-center md:px-10 md:py-40"
  >
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 cta-mist"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 55% 60% at 50% 110%, rgba(0,65,147,0.35) 0%, transparent 70%)"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 cta-mist-late"
      style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 45% at 20% 115%, rgba(62,142,222,0.16) 0%, transparent 70%)"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="relative" data-reveal>
      <p class="mono-label mb-6 !text-azure">// JOIN_US</p>
      <h2
        id="join-heading"
        class="mx-auto max-w-3xl font-display font-semibold leading-[1.12] tracking-[-0.015em] text-frost"
        style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem)"
      >
        에너지와 AI의 경계에서<br />함께 연구할 학생을 찾습니다
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-mist">
        학부 연구생 · 석사 과정 · 산학 인턴십. 궁금한 점은 언제든 편하게 문의해 주세요.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href={`mailto:${site.email}`} class="btn-primary">{site.email}</a>
        <a href={site.github} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-ghost">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-mist {
    animation: cta-drift 14s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  .cta-mist-late {
    animation: cta-drift-late 19s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  @keyframes cta-drift {
    from {
      transform: translateX(-6%);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(6%);
    }
  }
  @keyframes cta-drift-late {
    from {
      transform: translateX(8%);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(-8%);
    }
  }
  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .cta-mist,
    .cta-mist-late {
      animation: none;
    }
  }
</style>
